*****************************************************************               
*                                                               *               
*  SEXIPARM -- Parameters on entry to System EXIt routines.     *               
*              These dsects define the layout of the parameter  *               
*              area (XITSXPRM) containd in the dsect XITSAREA   *               
*              whose address is passed to the exit routine.     *               
*                                                               *               
*****************************************************************               
         SPACE 2                                                                
*                                                                               
* Supervisor Call Information                                                   
*                                                                               
         SPACE                                                                  
SEXITSVC RECORD BEGIN                                                           
SXISILC  DS    H             Supervisor Call Instruction length                 
SXISNUM  DS    H             Supervisor Call number                             
         END   ,                                                                
         SPACE 2                                                                
*                                                                               
* Program Interrupt Information                                                 
*                                                                               
         SPACE                                                                  
SEXITPI  RECORD BEGIN                                                           
SXIPILC  DS    H             Instruction Length                                 
SXIPCODE DS    H             Interrupt code                                     
SXIPEXA  DS    A             Exception address (codes 16 & 17)                  
         END   ,                                                                
         SPACE 2                                                                
*                                                                               
* Program Event Recording Information                                           
*                                                                               
         SPACE ,                                                                
SEXITPER RECORD BEGIN                                                           
SXIEILC  DS    H             Instruction Length                                 
SXIECODE DS    H             PER Code                                           
SXIEPERA DS    A             PER Address                                        
         END   ,                                                                
         SPACE 2                                                                
*                                                                               
* Monitor Call Information                                                      
*                                                                               
         SPACE ,                                                                
SEXITMC  RECORD BEGIN                                                           
SXIMILC  DS    H             Instruction Length                                 
SXIMCLA  DS    H             Monitor Class                                      
SXIMCODE DS    A             Monitor Code                                       
         END   ,                                                                
